column2: But  where  a  forcible  dispossession  has  taken  place

column1: within  a  period  of two  months  immediately  before  the  date  on  which  the

column2: information was filed under Section 66, he may make an order directing that

column1: the  party  dispossessed  be  restored  to  possession prohibiting  all  disturbance

column2: of such possession otherwise than under the  authority  of an  order or decree
